title: Utah DB Marcus Williams forces interception vs. Cal's Jared Goff
persons: Jared Goff Utah DB Marcus Williams
text:
Utah DB Marcus Williams forces interception vs. Cal's Jared Goff FOX Sports 
Oct 10, 2015 at 11:11p ET + 
Williams had two early forced turnovers vs. Cal on Saturday. Russ Isabella-USA TODAY Sports   11:11p ET 
Utah 's Marcus Williams made an early case for himself as the MVP of his showdown vs. the Bears on Saturday. 
Cal's quarterback Jared Goff , who's impressive play has earned Heisman speculation, entered the game with 15 TD's and just four interceptions. Early, however, Williams tipped and picked one of Goff's attempts. Williams returned the interception for 18 yards. It was his fourth interception of the season. true â€” College GameDay (@CollegeGameDay) October 11, 2015 
Later in the first quarter, Williams also added a fumble recovery for his second takeaway of the game.
